@node "Limitations" "Limitations"


   Limitations




   There is not many limitations against the PC version anymore,
   but there are some


   * Log sending not implemented, and will probably not be
     implemented. But as long as there is some pc Oratory
     users online, noone should miss this funktion, as long
     as the logs are recieved.

   * Current topic will NOT be SENT to the people who joins,
     but that shouldn't be a problem if there are PC users
     online. Topic changes is working

   * Since not working, that means that you'll not be able
     to see ar send information about how long you and
     others have been online or at the current state

   * Ignoring of others messages not possible

   * No sound when recieving beepmessages, only info about it
     -and that may be just as good... :)


   Most of the other is working.
@endnode

